---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base>
  <header class="pt-5 pb-1">
    <a href="#top" class="flex items-center gap-3 no-underline text-slate-100">
      <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand to-brand-soft grid place-items-center shadow-soft">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 26 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="g1" x1="0" y1="0" x2="26" y2="26" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
              <stop stop-color="#22d3ee"/>
              <stop offset="1" stop-color="#60a5fa"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <circle cx="10" cy="13" r="8" stroke="url(#g1)" stroke-width="2" opacity=".7"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="13" r="8" stroke="url(#g1)" stroke-width="2" opacity=".7"/>
          <path d="M7 13.2l3.3 3.3L19 8.8" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <h1 class="m-0 text-sm sm:text-base tracking-wide">The Familiar Choice Method™</h1>
    </a>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="card mt-4 p-5 sm:p-7 md:p-10">
    <p class="uppercase tracking-[.14em] text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] font-bold text-brand">Familiarity + Visibility = Calls</p>
    

<!-- Headline -->
<h2 class="hero-title text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mt-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand to-brand-soft bg-clip-text text-transparent">
  Every call is up for grabs.  Will they choose you?
</h2>

<p class="text-base md:text-[18px] text-slate-300/90 mt-4">
  A simple framework for local service businesses to stop competing as strangers and start becoming the familiar, trusted choice.
</p>

<!-- Buttons wrapper -->
<div class="cta-buttons flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mt-6">
  <a class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto justify-center items-center gap-2 font-bold no-underline rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-brand text-[#002033] shadow-soft border border-transparent hover:brightness-105 active:scale-[.99] transition"
     href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rohit-singh-atx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
     Connect on LinkedIn
  </a>
  <a class="inline-flex w-full sm:w-auto justify-center items-center gap-2 font-semibold no-underline rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-transparent text-slate-100 border border-slate-700/80 hover:bg-slate-800/40 transition"
     href="mailto:rohit.singh@localiq.com">
     Email Rohit
  </a>
</div>
</section>

  <!-- TWO CARDS -->
  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-7 mt-8">
    <article class="card p-5 sm:p-6 md:p-8">
      <span class="pill">RELATIONAL MEDIA</span>
      <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold mt-2">Build familiarity <em>before</em> the search</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-[15px]">
        <li>Branding, social, YouTube, radio, billboards, retargeting</li>
        <li>Creates repeated exposure → recognition → trust</li>
        <li>Reduces perceived risk and makes you feel like a safe choice</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-3 p-3 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-100 text-sm">
        <strong>Goal:</strong> Move from unknown → familiar → trusted.
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-5 sm:p-6 md:p-8">
      <span class="pill">DIRECTIONAL MEDIA</span>
      <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold mt-2">Capture demand <em>at</em> the search</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-[15px]">
        <li>Google Ads (PPC), Local SEO, call extensions</li>
        <li>Show up when customers actively search (e.g., “AC repair near me”)</li>
        <li>Turns familiarity into calls, appointments, and revenue</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-3 p-3 rounded-xl border border-sky-500/30 bg-sky-400/10 text-sky-100 text-sm">
        <strong>Rule of thumb:</strong> Start here if budget is tight; add Relational to tip the scales.
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <!-- VENN -->
<section class="venn card mt-8 p-6 md:p-8">
    <div class="grid place-items-center p-1 sm:p-2">
      <svg class="w-full max-w-[620px] md:max-w-[680px] h-auto" viewBox="0 0 680 260" role="img" aria-labelledby="vennTitle vennDesc">
        <title id="vennTitle">Relational + Directional = Familiar Choice</title>
        <desc id="vennDesc">Two overlapping circles labeled Relational and Directional; the overlap is labeled Familiar Choice.</desc>
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="rel" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0" stop-color="#22d3ee" stop-opacity=".18"/>
            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#22d3ee" stop-opacity=".08"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <linearGradient id="dir" x1="1" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0" stop-color="#60a5fa" stop-opacity=".18"/>
            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#60a5fa" stop-opacity=".08"/>
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <circle cx="230" cy="130" r="100" fill="url(#rel)" stroke="#22d3ee" stroke-opacity=".35" stroke-width="2"/>
        <circle cx="450" cy="130" r="100" fill="url(#dir)" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-opacity=".35" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="230" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8b3cf" font-size="16" font-family="Inter,system-ui">RELATIONAL</text>
        <text x="450" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a8b3cf" font-size="16" font-family="Inter,system-ui">DIRECTIONAL</text>
        <rect x="290" y="108" rx="10" ry="10" width="100" height="44" fill="#0b1222" stroke="#1f2937"/>
        <text x="340" y="135" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e5e7eb" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter,system-ui">FAMILIAR CHOICE</text>
      </svg>
      <p class="text-center text-slate-300/80 text-xs sm:text-sm mt-2">
        Relational builds trust before the search.  Directional captures demand at the search.  Together, they make you the familiar choice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="card mt-6 sm:mt-7 p-5 sm:p-6">
    <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold">About Rohit Singh</h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-slate-200 text-sm sm:text-[15px]">
      For 15 years, I’ve helped local service businesses understand a simple truth: every call is up for grabs.  When life triggers a search, customers don’t always pick the “best” provider — they pick the one that feels familiar and safe.  That’s what <strong>The Familiar Choice Method™</strong> is built to create.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm sm:text-[15px]">
      Want to apply it to your business? <a class="link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rohit-singh-atx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Connect on LinkedIn</a> or <a class="link" href="mailto:rohit.singh@localiq.com">email me</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
